headline: ExchangeRight Fully Subscribes $62 Million Net-Leased Portfolio 69 DST, Expanding Essential Income REIT Pipeline
summary: PASADENA, Calif., August 04, 2025--ExchangeRight has announced the full subscription of Net-Leased Portfolio 69 DST, reflecting continued demand for the company’s historically recession-resilient, diversified net-leased offerings that support ExchangeRight’s Essential Income REIT’s growing acquisition pipeline. The $62 million portfolio of net-leased real estate, backed by primarily investment-grade companies operating in necessity-based industries, provides investors with monthly distributions

headline: The SPAM® Brand Hits the Road with SPAM® Sushi as Store Availability Goes Nationwide
summary: The SPAM® brand, in collaboration with Kroger, is turning heads this summer — and they're doing it in style. Earlier this year, SPAM® sushi products rolled out nationwide at Kroger's Family Stores, including Ralphs Grocery Company, and now they're hitting the road to celebrate in true SPAM® brand style! Introducing the first-ever SPAM® Musubi Mobile: a larger-than-life food truck shaped like a SPAM® Musubi that's nearly seven feet tall — an unmistakable site for fans and musubi lovers alike.

headline: American Consumers Are Getting Thrifty Again
summary: Generic brands and bulk buying are on the rise and fewer fancy burritos are being sold. “The ‘what the heck’ purchase is completely gone.”
